{"product_id":"hoia-brightening-vitamin-c-serum","title":"HOIA Brightening Vitamin C Serum","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVitamin C serum contains various derivatives of vitamin C, vitamin E, hyaluronic acid, niacinamide and algae. It helps to neutralize free radicals in the skin, repair and protect it from environmental stress, such as sun damage. It helps to rejuvenate and brighten skin, stimulate collagen synthesis, reduce and prevent the formation of pigmentation spots, even out skin tone, relieve redness. This serum is fast absorbing and suitable for all skin types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply to clean skin and massage until absorbed. Also suitable to use in sunburnt areas, mix it with your daily moisturizer or body cream right before use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Citrus Aurantium Amara Flower water, 3-0-Ethyl Ascorbic acid, Ascorbyl Tetraisopalmitate, Sargassum Fluitans\/Natans extract, Niacinamide, Aqua, Glycerin, Tocopherol-Acetate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydronated Sodium Hyaluronate, Pentylene Glycol, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Levulinate, Citric Acid. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324614086983,"sku":null,"price":44.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-brightening-vitamin-c-serum-302190.jpg?v=1739897238","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hoia-brightening-vitamin-c-serum","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}